// useTheme
// Provides the current UI theme and controls to change or toggle it.

Theme is stored in the UI store, which persists it to localStorage automatically.

FUNCTION useTheme() -> { theme, setTheme, toggleTheme }                         EXPORT
  CALLS: useUIStore (uiStore)
  Reads theme, setTheme, and toggleTheme from the UI store using shallow comparison.
  Returns memoized wrappers for setTheme and toggleTheme.
